description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 51, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 255, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 2 for East, Box for South, and 3 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60515-12430-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [255 Votes, Top 5% Score]
